data.title: VH1
data.meta_description: VH1 was originally created by Warner-Amex Satellite Entertainment, at the time a division of Warner Communications and the original owner of MTV and Nickelodeon, and launched on January 1, 1985, in the former space of Turner Broadcasting System's short-lived Cable Music Channel. Designed by LPG...
